headline: Is EMCOR Group (EME) Still Attractively Priced After Its Strong Multi‑Year Share Price Rally
summary: If you are wondering whether EMCOR Group's current share price still offers value, you are not alone, especially after such a strong run in recent years. The stock last closed at US$716.28, with returns of 4.1% over the past week, 14.2% over the past month, 12.2% year to date, 63.8% over the past year and roughly 7x over the past five years.
